      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Dreyfus cannot make the first attack on anyone he is bound to by guest-right within a space he has been invited into. Harald invited him inside as his hound; after Harald made a hostile move (hunting knife), guest-right is void. If the PCs ever invite Dreyfus into a space, note it — the guest-right binding applies there too.</p>",
          "director": ""
        },
