      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>At the start of combat, Dreyfus identifies the hero with the highest Presence (targets first — most dangerous in conversation) and the hero with the highest Might (avoids melee with them unless cornered). He has listened to the party for the entirety of their mission and knows their fighting styles.</p>",
