        "lastModifiedBy": null
      },
      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>When Dreyfus reaches half Stamina (30 or below), he immediately uses Shape-Shift to take raven form and attempts to flee through the nearest window, chimney, or gap. He uses his full movement to exit the building. He cannot be stopped by free strikes in raven form. He escapes — this is intentional, he reappears in Beat 24. Note exactly what the party did to him; those specific injuries will manifest in his degraded form fifteen beats later.</p>",
          "director": ""
        },
        "source": {
          "book": "Svellheim Campaign (Era of Embers)",
          "page": "",
          "license": ""
        },
